sceneActions.name: Are they excluded by any funds?
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH path=(i:Issuer)-[:IS_PART_OF*]-(matEnt:Entity)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]->(exce:excEntity)<-[ee:EXCLUDES_ENTITY]-()
WHERE id(i) IN $nodes
RETURN path

sceneActions.name: Show me all the related countries
sceneActions.cypher:
OPTIONAL MATCH path=(e:Entity)-->(c:Country)
WHERE id(e) IN $nodes
RETURN path

sceneActions.name: Are they sanctioned by any committees?
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH path=(i:Issuer)-[:IS_PART_OF*]-(matEnt:Entity)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]->(sanc:sancEntity)<-[ee:SANCTIONS]-()
WHERE id(i) IN $nodes
RETURN path

sceneActions.name: Show me additional entity insights (location, industry)
sceneActions.cypher:
OPTIONAL MATCH path=(in:Industry)<--(i:Entity)-->(c:Country)
WHERE id(i) IN $nodes
return path

sceneActions.name: Is there any insights from reports/news?
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH path=(i:Entity)-[:IS_MOST_SIMILAR_TO_META]->(m:metaEntity)-[]-()
WHERE id(i) IN $nodes
return path

sceneActions.name: Show the impacted portfolios by a sanction committee
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH (p:Committee), (f:Fund)
WHERE id(p) IN $nodes AND id(f) IN $nodes
RETURN p, apoc.create.vRelationship(p,'IS_IMPACTED',{},f) as rel, f

sceneActions.name: Show me the direct EXCLUSION connection
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH path = SHORTEST 1 (i:Issuer)-[:IS_PART_OF|IS_SIMILAR_TO]-+(e:excEntity)
WHERE id(i) IN $nodes AND id(e) IN $nodes
RETURN i, apoc.create.vRelationship(i,'IS_CONNECTED_TO',{},e) as rel, e

sceneActions.name: Show me the direct SANCTION connection
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH path = SHORTEST 1 (i:Issuer)-[:IS_PART_OF|IS_SIMILAR_TO]-+(e:sancEntity)
WHERE id(i) IN $nodes AND id(e) IN $nodes
RETURN i, apoc.create.vRelationship(i,'IS_CONNECTED_TO',{},e) as rel, e

templates.name: [TOTAL] Portfolio risk exposure (INDIRECT SANCTION)
templates.text: Does $FundName hold any assets INDIRECTLY sanctioned?
templates.cypher:
MATCH p=(ff:Fund {name: $FundName})-[h:HOLDS]->(a:Asset)-[:IS_ISSUED_BY]->(i:Issuer)-[:IS_PART_OF*]-(matEnt:Entity)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]->(sace:sancEntity)<-[:SANCTIONS]-(c:Committee)
WHERE h.amount > 0
RETURN p

templates.cypher:
MATCH path=(f:Fund{name: $FundName})-[r:HOLDS]->(a:Asset)-->(:Issuer)
where r.amount > 100000000
return path

templates.name: Insight 1. Issuer overview
templates.cypher:
match p1=(i:Issuer)<-[:IS_ISSUED_BY]-(a:Asset)<-[:HOLDS]-(f:Fund)
match p2=(c:Country)<--(i)-[:BELONGS_TO]->(ind:Industry)
where i.name = $IssuerName
return p1, p2

templates.name: [TOP] Indirect sanction
templates.text: Show me top $n companies we invest that are INDIRECTLY sanctioned
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n:Fund)-[h:HOLDS WHERE h.amount>1000000]->(a:Asset)-[:IS_ISSUED_BY]->(e)-[:IS_PART_OF*]-(matEnt:Entity)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]-(sanc:sancEntity)<-[r:SANCTIONS]-(c)
WHERE h.amount > 1000000
WITH DISTINCT e, h.amount as amount
ORDER BY h.amount DESC
LIMIT $n
MATCH path=(e)-[:IS_PART_OF*]-(matEnt:Entity)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]-(sanc:sancEntity)<-[ee:SANCTIONS]-()
RETURN path

templates.name: [TOP] Direct sanction
templates.text: Show me top $n companies we invest that are DIRECTLY sanctioned
templates.cypher:
MATCH (f:Fund)-[h:HOLDS]->(a:Asset)-[iib:IS_ISSUED_BY]->(e:Entity)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]-(sanc:sancEntity)-[r:SANCTIONS]-(c)
WHERE h.amount > 1000000
WITH DISTINCT e, h.amount as amount
ORDER BY h.amount DESC
LIMIT $n
MATCH path=(e)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]-(sanc:sancEntity)<-[ee:SANCTIONS]-()
RETURN path

templates.name: Demo insight 3
templates.text: Show me top $n companies we invest that are INDIRECTLY excluded by other funds for $reason
templates.cypher:
MATCH (f:Fund)-[h:HOLDS]->(a:Asset)-[iib:IS_ISSUED_BY]->(e:Entity)-[:IS_PART_OF*]-(matEnt:Entity)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]-(exc:excEntity)-[r:EXCLUDES_ENTITY]-(of)
WHERE h.amount > 1000000
AND r.mainCategory = $reason
WITH DISTINCT e, h.amount as amount, collect(of.name) as otherFunds
ORDER BY h.amount DESC
LIMIT $n
MATCH path=(e)-[:IS_PART_OF*]-(matEnt:Entity)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]-(:excEntity)-[ee:EXCLUDES_ENTITY]-(of)
WHERE NOT (of)-[:HOLDS]-()
AND ee.mainCategory = $reason
RETURN path

templates.name: Demo insight 2
templates.text: Show me top $n companies we invest that are DIRECTLY excluded by other funds for $reason
templates.cypher:
MATCH (f:Fund)-[h:HOLDS]->(a:Asset)-[iib:IS_ISSUED_BY]->(e:Entity)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]-(exc:excEntity)-[r:EXCLUDES_ENTITY]-(of)
WHERE h.amount > 1000000
AND r.mainCategory = $reason
WITH DISTINCT e, h.amount as amount, collect(of.name) as otherFunds
ORDER BY h.amount DESC
LIMIT $n
MATCH path=(e)-[:IS_SIMILAR_TO]-(:excEntity)-[ee:EXCLUDES_ENTITY]-(of)
WHERE NOT (of)-[:HOLDS]-()
AND ee.mainCategory = $reason
RETURN path
